This is a collection of Talespin episodes released on DVD
All audio tracks have been included and A/V quality kept
as good as possible while still compressing from 62 Gbit
to 17 Gbit.

Languages: Swedish, English, Danish, German, Italian, Norwegian

The DVD releases contained almost all episodes from 1 to 54
(out of 65) but excluded following 4 episodes:
  Talespin 05 - From Here to Machinery
  Talespin 12 - Vowel Play
  Talespin 24 - A Touch of Glass
  Talespin 48 - Jumping the Guns

text documents with these filenames are just created as placeholders.


Please SEED until 2.0. I am not sure how long I can share this, so help wanted.
